Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.23,0:01:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Miss Donburi Contest \Nfinally starts tomorrow, Pastel. {Donburi Island (どんぶり島 Donburi-tō?) is a location in the TwinBee series. It is an island in the Pacific Ocean that serves as the main setting for most of the adventures that take place in the series. It is in this place where Dr. Cinnamon has settled his laboratory, and also where his family and friends live.; donburi = porcelain bowl}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.75,0:01:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think I can win! \NI should probably just withdraw.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.56,0:01:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that, Pastel?! Are you going to\Nlet all that effort{blood, sweat, and tears } you’ve poured into this {up until today }go to waste?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.96,0:01:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear the passionate cries\Nof encouragement coming from your fans?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.71,0:01:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{was: BEE? - I assume twinBEE's shtick or something?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.41,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Light...? {ignoring -kun -san because they have english names}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.76,0:01:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when do you talk like {\i1}that{\i0}?! {??? was: I think that was supposed to BEE a legitimate form of speech.}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.61,0:01:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Pastel, there's something\NI want you to test for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.22,0:01:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My newest creation! \NI just baked my first batch.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.48,0:01:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like it, I might add it to the menu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.56,0:02:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They look delicious! I'll try one.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.91,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.27,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee, how many\Ncalories does this cookie have?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.18,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me just a sec...\N Um, it should bee 20 calories!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.92,0:02:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Then you can eat half of it, Pastel.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.45,0:02:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I can't even enjoy {\i1}one{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}measly cookie?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.60,0:02:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They look so good though... \NWell then, I'll give half to WinBee.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.27,0:02:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.85,0:02:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.75,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it, Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.61,0:02:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s like... eating tokoroten in Santa Monica. \NWeirdly unique, you know? {lit: to give you an analogy, ... , a never-before experienced taste - tokoroten is not eaten anywhere except japan so eating it in california would feel very unusual hence this analogy}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.60,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Ma-Madoka...?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We'll be leaving now, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{And we're off! We'll train our running\Nand crawling all the way to the lab!} {?????????? running and ****} And we're off! We'll do our running \N and crawling training all the way to the lab!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Again?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No complaining! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why're you so \N impatient to get there, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.72,0:03:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gulp!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.11,0:03:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? When did everybody leave? How rude.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.22,0:03:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Madoka, do you know where\Nthat potion I made earlier ran off to? {/medicine}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it's some kind of\Nweird creation again anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are a harsh granddaughter.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.09,0:04:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! It's perfect! \NWhat a genius of a scientist I am!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.42,0:04:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ZakoBee, how're\Nthe repairs going over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.64,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll still take a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.31,0:04:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you dumb?! What are you even doing down there?\NIt must be ready by tomorrow's contest!{\i0}{?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, I get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.90,0:04:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh...\NOne of these days, I'm replacing them.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.38,0:04:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, she completely fell for my trick. \NGirls are just like that, after all. {??? wagahai no *** ni - maybe he orchestrated the whole contest or something?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, \NI get TwinBee as a bonus prize! {I assume twinbee is a personal name of one of those machines, not a type, like "one of the twinbees"}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's most unusual.\NHow did this happen?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.89,0:05:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how tiny they've gotten!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.05,0:05:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute... W-We're screwed! {what should we do}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.67,0:05:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In this condition, there's no way\Nshe'll be able to be in the contest!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.33,0:05:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Instead of worrying about the contest, \Ncan't you worry about {\i1}me{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}for once?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.45,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You're so insensitive!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.66,0:05:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, Light? It's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.46,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Madoka? \NIs something the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.52,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Say, isn't something strange happening?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange how?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.96,0:06:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, maybe...\Nlike a severe change in someone's body?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! Hurry up and\Nchange us back to normal already! {hakase }
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.65,0:06:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, sorry about all this. I can easily\Nchange you back with this magnifying ray gun.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind the explanations,\Njust hurry up and do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.52,0:06:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Be patient, dear. \NThis gun runs on bell-power. {https://twinbee.fandom.com/wiki/Bell}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.62,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, but could you get me a bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're hopeless.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Something the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc! The clouds! {because Bell Power-Ups usually appear on the battlefield by shooting at Bell Clouds on the scenery that hide them}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds?\NWhat is it about the clouds, Light?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The clouds are gone!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.30,0:06:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's not good... Huh? {?? komatta? kumotta? a mix of both?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.51,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a single cloud within a 60 km radius...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.89,0:06:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! That's where the clouds are gathering.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.64,0:07:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like an old castle to me, \Nbut what's a thing like that doing up there? {castle wall; town walls; defensive wall; rampart}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.79,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit Castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.67,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be the Legendary Spirit Castle.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit Castle?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.02,0:07:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Is it like an air-island?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.48,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is that our Donburi Archipelago\Nused to have one more island in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.72,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it was last seen 800 years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And on that island lived a queen \Nwho governed the entire archipelago.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.83,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But that queen couldn't be satisfied until she \N was prettier than and high above everyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.82,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She ended up building her own castle \Nthat floated in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.84,0:07:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is she\Nhoarding all of our clouds now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.15,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even I don't know the answer to that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.83,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, unless we get some bells, \Nwe can't change Pastel back!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.57,0:08:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we can't change her back, \Nthen that also means she can't be in the contest!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the timely explanation!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Pastel! I swear I'll get you \Nback to normal in no time!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.80,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, TwinBee Team! \NHurry to the Spirit Castle!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.91,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no more than three hours \Nuntil the contest starts.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.96,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll have to get it done before that.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you talking beeg as usual!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.64,0:08:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.64,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Now's not the time for bickering.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.36,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the Spirit Castle?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.40,0:08:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If we continue on this course, we'll get intercepted by an anti-aircraft beam like Fork Eye. {?????? believing the wiki subs, no mention of this fooku aiai on wiki or anywhere}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.23,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even so, we don't exactly have\Na better strategy for sneaking inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Can't you think of anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.28,Overlap,,0,0,0,,There's the beam!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the beam is trying to shoot us down now!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.55,0:09:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, figures! {???? was: THANKS FOR LETTING US KNOW!}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.07,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They dodged it?! Their agility is far \N greater than that of the previous invaders.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.11,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they? \NWhy are they closing in on us?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.98,0:09:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fuss. I shall ask them for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.02,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?\NThey suddenly stopped shooting.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.07,0:09:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...\NLet's try goin' in through there!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alert! Energy surge detected ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.21,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the beeg idea?! \NYou're not fighting fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.08,0:10:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Why are you trying\Nto invade Queen Juliana's castle? {https://twinbee.fandom.com/wiki/Juliana}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.05,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We could ask the same of you! \NWhy are you hogging all the bell clouds to yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. You want some of our bell clouds?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are very important to the queen!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall be punished!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.37,0:10:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Light? Light! \NWhy aren't you flying up to fight back?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.51,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do! {itadaki?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.77,0:10:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go! {sore}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.95,0:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy-peasy!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.99,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl {\i1}still{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}hasn't shown up?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.85,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly hope I didn't forget anything. {/overlook}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No wait! Stop! Let me explain myself! {????????}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.48,0:11:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know what it is,\Nbut it sure is pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.28,0:11:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Look at that! So many bells!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Bells! We got the bells!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.95,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee, how much time do we have left?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty more minutes.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.54,0:12:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess we'd better leave.\NEven if we still have no idea what's going on here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.24,0:12:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.97,0:12:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Bells! The bells!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.74,0:12:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the big idea, scaring us like that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,GwinBee!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.90,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn, now you're getting it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{here you go?}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{ta-daa!}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.09,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up! Why did you kick me out? \NExplain yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna know that badly, I'll show you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Off you go! {lit: go and fly!}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.61,0:13:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you \Nnot to use me as a projectile?! {lit: not to throw me}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.78,0:14:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we might as well go this way... \NThe other route is blocked off anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.21,0:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, come to think of it, we left GwinBee beehind. \NGwinBee, where are you now?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.64,0:14:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back at the glowing room...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. Well, catch up with us soon, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better beelieve it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.78,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this grandma's corpse?! \NIs this the queen we've been running around here for?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light! Look at that!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.79,0:15:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! She's {\i1}hot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.02,0:15:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might you children be?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.73,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to my soldiers? {servants}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Soldiers? You mean that\Nballoon guy and that lightning guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.99,0:15:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say\Nyou defeated Raijin and Fujin? {gods of lighting and wind in buddhist pantheon}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.09,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, it seems you’ve bought me\Nsome time to prepare for my resurrection.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.24,0:15:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on... I don't really get \Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.57,0:15:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Queen Juliana.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.88,0:15:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My beauty is eternal.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.36,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the power of bell clouds \Nis required to maintain my beauty.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.60,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To that end, I awaken once \Nevery 400 years to summon the clouds
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.76,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and use up all of that bell power \Nto preserve my beauty.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.27,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, it's a major problem! \NPut the clouds back the way they were!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.77,0:16:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should I? Tell me, Bean Girl. {lit: minimum little girl}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.65,0:16:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bean Girl? \NDon't you have any sympathy?! {lit: even though I'm so much in trouble}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.40,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't you worry about her! \NJust ignore this little inconv—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.34,0:16:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished replenishing my beauty.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.44,0:16:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that you leave this island at once \Nsince I'm going back to sleep now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished replenishing it? So then... {the clouds will be released now}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.96,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear not. The bell clouds shall return to the skies of Donburi in good time.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.21,0:16:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! That's a relief. \NSo I guess I'll be able to change back eventually.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.77,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, what time is it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.35,0:16:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.88,0:16:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! It's this late already? \NMiss Donburi is gonna start any minute!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.66,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Donburi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What's happening?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.29,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Donburi—that is {\i1}me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.64,0:17:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall not tolerate that anyone else in the\Nworld be declared more beautiful than I!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth! To the Miss Donburi Contest venue!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.03,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That dirty hag... I'll get ya \N for treating us like that! Let's go! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew... those are tough! \NOkay, next!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.18,0:17:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.61,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! So arrogant!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.45,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to smash you?! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.18,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here it comes.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.85,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, another one!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.31,0:18:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you. And you. And you! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is never-ending.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.47,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then it's carpet bombing time!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.00,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Make it stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.00,0:18:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What?! I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! {/how did it come to this}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.99,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell is Mint when we need him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.00,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint! Mint! Everyone's calling on you. \NWe'd better bee going!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.51,0:19:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.39,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what'll I do with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.56,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, I don't have\Ntime to waste fighting these!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get Pastel in that contest!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.57,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Light... Thanks. \NBut you don't have to do it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.54,0:19:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I {\i1}absolutely{\i0} \Nhave to be in the contest anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.08,0:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't just give up so easily!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.54,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream of becoming\NMiss Donburi isn't yours alone! {does this read awkward?}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.84,0:19:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, even Light says nice things, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Light?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where were you all this time? {lit: where did you come from now}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.84,0:20:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the Spirit Castle!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.14,0:20:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were inside the castle, \Nyou should've at least sabotaged it, you idiot! {lit: break something}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.88,0:20:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...{Marty: I was thinking of switching it to "My bee-ad..." to make it punny but idk if that'd work; pere: eh}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.57,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, the enemy has multiplied. {lit: their number has increased}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.35,0:20:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What bothersome pests. {??? haedakoto?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Give them a taste of our\NCrazy Night attack at full power. {???? maybe crazy night, maybe koreijo inai to = the attack they'll never see again?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.12,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.91,0:20:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, to think you were chilling \Nin the castle while we were fighting! Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.09,0:20:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint refused to leave\Nwithout it, so I had to take it...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But it certainly is pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.92,0:20:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! They're preparing\Nfor another beam attack! {lit: shining attack}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.11,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.04,0:20:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not another beam attack? {?????? pikapika? betabeta?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.79,0:20:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.84,0:21:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, my queen! \NThe generator is going wild!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The main coil is gone! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy leak cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.41,0:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So many, so shiny! {??????? piccaribee? maybe nothing at all?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.34,Top,,0,0,0,,{One, two, three, four.}{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.54,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you decide who Miss Donburi is, \Nwhile I, the prettiest woman to ever live, am absent!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.64,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we've got more than enough bells!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.33,0:21:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pastel! Pastel, can you hear me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.06,0:21:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can, Madoka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.48,0:21:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The contest has already started!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.62,0:21:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What should we do, Light?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.72,0:21:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get the bells?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.03,0:21:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.94,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then hurry! Grandpa will\Nbring the magnifying gun with him!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.88,0:22:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.12,0:22:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Light!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.94,0:22:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Step on it, TwinBee!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.70,0:22:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, thank you, thank you. \NThat was Kumiko with a lovely ponytail.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.92,0:22:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, let us continue \Nwith entry number 15, Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.91,0:22:32.93,Top,,0,0,0,,Pastel? Huh? Pastel? Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.83,0:22:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Pastel! She didn't make it in time!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all {\i1}your{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}fault, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.32,0:22:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.92,0:22:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the participant seems to be absent, \Na disqualification is...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.40,0:22:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry number 15, Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.41,0:23:03.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Madoka-chan? Hurry up and change me back!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.53,0:23:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She's late! Too late!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.18,0:23:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, they've just appeared!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.61,0:23:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Both she and TwinBee? All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.00,0:23:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee! Over here! \NThrow us the bells, quick!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.67,0:23:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye! Get some!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.74,0:23:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, how do I aim this thing? {????? lit: over there? or doing this?}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.18,0:23:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I can see her perfectly!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa! Just do it already!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.34,0:23:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! Seriously, stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.76,0:23:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{????? mou, **** nanoni; maybe something like "Geez! Even though I've been preparing for this for so long!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.41,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,10 points, 9 points,\N9 points, 9 points, and 10 points!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.00,0:23:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry number 13 has\Nreceived a sudden surge of points!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.63,0:24:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspected something like this might happen, \Nso I placed another grabber! {/arm}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.91,0:24:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What a genius of a scientist I am!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.85,0:24:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel! No!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:13.74,0:24:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Grandpa, can't you aim better?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:17.24,0:24:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help. \NTry aiming a little more to the right.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.14,0:24:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You idiot! {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.84,0:24:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:29.99,0:24:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This time, it's number 14, Kumiko! {even though it said "7" on her swimsuit}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:33.28,0:24:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,10 points, 9 points,\N10 points, 10 points, 9 points!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.56,0:24:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.91,0:24:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.99,0:24:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind me. I never expected it \Nto work out anyway. That's the kind of role I play.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:51.31,0:24:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't even have any budget to speak of this time. \NThe sky is beautiful in itself, they say. {??? meaning some things are perfect as they are, without even trying or doing anything special - probably referring to himself?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:56.22,0:24:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.01,0:24:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mesmerizing... {subarashi?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.01,0:24:59.87,Top,,0,0,0,,Now I can never get married! {meaning no one will take her as a bride because everyone saw her naked now}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:00.58,0:25:03.26,Top,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do now?! {??? maybe "why did you do this"}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:00.85,0:25:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! If I get magnified too, \Nthe same thing will happen to me! {lit: get showered in this}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.25,0:25:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka! It's your fault I missed! \NJust sit there and don't interfere!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.38,0:25:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:12.70,0:25:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop it! Don't shoot me!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.74,0:25:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.81,0:25:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No looking!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.72,0:25:28.08,Top,,0,0,0,,10 points, 10 points, 10 points, 10 points, 10 points!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:28.08,0:25:29.95,Top,,0,0,0,,An absolute perfect score! {lit: without complaints, perfect}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.95,0:25:36.22,Top,,0,0,0,,The winner of this year's Miss Donburi Contest\Nis entry number 15, Pastel! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:34.56,0:25:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.22,0:25:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Now that motorcycle is mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.20,0:25:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, what's that about a motorcycle?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.74,0:25:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, you see, if you're chosen as Miss Donburi, \Nyou get a Yamasaki Gaia 400 as a bonus prize! {parody of Kawasaki Ninja 400?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.76,0:25:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And since you can't ride motorcycles, \Nyou'll let me have it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.70,0:25:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that's what this all was about?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:58.48,0:26:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{And here I was thinking that your excitement \Nabout this contest was suspicious...} So I was right... your excitement about \N this contest was suspicious, after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:03.21,0:26:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? P-Pastel? I'm sure\Nwe can work this out with words.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.17,0:26:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go! Put something on. \NWe don't want you catching a cold, do we? Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:20.15,0:26:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how much {\i1}you{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}enjoy being big! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.86,0:26:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:24.27,0:26:25.63,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Give that to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.88,0:26:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No! W-Wait... Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:31.90,0:26:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{ouch?}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:36.54,0:26:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:37.41,0:26:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, he's too nimble. {??????? ecchi? komatta? }
Dialogue: 10,0:26:39.41,0:26:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's crank this thing up! {?????? something about increasing something}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:46.09,0:26:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to my bike, Pastel?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.68,0:26:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! {?? over there = caught him?}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:01.23,0:27:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Miss... Donburi...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.34,0:27:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:09.80,0:27:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's the main coil of the generator...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.42,0:27:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:18.20,0:27:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.24,0:27:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's saying that you can have\Nthis diadem because you're so pretty.{She cries after this. Is it because she's overjoyed to have received such a comment or because she got called an old lady? -Marty; pere: the latter if I had to guess}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:26.92,0:27:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a nice boy, Mint.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:29.76,0:27:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When you grow up, \Nthe ladies will all bee crazy about you.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:32.94,0:27:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:35.05,0:27:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:02.51,0:28:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Starring: TwinBee—Mayumi Tanaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.49,0:28:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel! Did everyone enjoy it? \NHekiru Shiina.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:10.03,0:28:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,WinBee—Kumiko Nishihara.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.54,0:28:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint and GwinBee—Miki Ito.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:15.83,0:28:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Cinnamon—Kazumi Tanaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:18.97,0:28:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka—Mariko Kouda.
